{"tid":1183614,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"驚險！廢老捐車罅過路　下秒慘被輾腳倒地","createTime":"2019-06-03T05:11:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-03T08:10:17.000Z","uid":225464,"like":24,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"10d15b92f0a672795ff8fa78458cfae1cd336a08","tid":1183614,"uid":225464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-03T05:11:31.000Z","msg":"驚險！廢老捐車罅過路 下秒慘被輾腳倒地<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2MnGhMb\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2MnGhMb&d=oOXZKU%2BZRanU2kHQSwewOIkJ8G0wCzjK2GZdEgWvKr0%3D&h=60c891ec\" target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2MnGhMb</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190603/photo/bkn-20190603123147180-0603_00822_001_01p.jpg?20190603125806\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190603%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190603123147180-0603_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20190603125806&h=bb314b74&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n睇片都覺得痛&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上周六（1日）下午約1時半，有大叔在建業街近熟食中心位置橫過馬路時，未留意到有私家車駛至，左腳疑遭輾過，撞向側鏡後跌倒在地。<br />\n<br />\n有目擊者留言指：「我見個司機問咗個阿叔：『你真係冇事？咁我走啦』，個阿叔當時坐喺路邊着鞋&hellip;最後個司機走咗，冇事發生」。"},{"pid":"7d7ed48b7cd2c8b303c620c33465db9a3a188c72","tid":1183614,"uid":225464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-03T05:11:48.000Z","msg":"咁都無事！？"},{"pid":"64851193f76fb35cd3322515821a7a14eb6332ed","tid":1183614,"uid":19055,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-03T05:14:15.000Z","msg":"抵撚死，唔撚睇車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3ecc79d97195f70597f20e7421f6973639a3474","tid":1183614,"uid":48334,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-03T05:14:35.000Z","msg":"無敵金鋼腿"},{"pid":"7a17b776ba1d3e2286ad35172554c3e2609f63e1","tid":1183614,"uid":63909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-03T05:15:07.000Z","msg":"片呢"},{"pid":"ae814433c182a23647d68d42f676fa83fa394c54","tid":1183614,"uid